# CVE-2026-48712: protobufjs uncontrolled recursion (CWE-674)
#
# Backport adapted for protobufjs 8.0.3 after CVE-2026-45740.
# Depth-limit changes from CVE-2026-45740 (util.checkDepth) are retained;
# this patch adds the remaining 48712 hardening delta only.
#
